Step 1. AWS Credentials

aws configure



Step 2. Save The Grouping of OS In a File

ansible-inventory -i /root/ec2.aws_ec2.yaml --list | jq 'keys' > /root/ec2_groups.txt



Step 3. Run The Ansible Playbook

ansible-playbook -i /root/ec2.aws_ec2.yaml /root/playbook.yaml



Step 4. Check The Status of The Packages On Ubuntu OS

systemctl status nginx
systemctl status tomcat10
systemctl status mysql



Step 5. Check The Status Of The Packages on Amazon Linux OS

systemctl status nginx
systemctl status tomcat10
systemctl status MySQL
